{"tid":2069761,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"個心裂咗","createTime":"2020-06-18T15:37:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T17:04:35.000Z","uid":255814,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ec9ec9fb43d52f13926b0a5a065ea420a4ee8532","tid":2069761,"uid":255814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:37:48.000Z","msg":"眼白白睇住你online同另一個傾計<br />\n自己乜都做唔到<br />\n好想放低你 點解又要捉住我<br />\n點解死都要一齊上堂reg科<br />\n明明大家今個sem都要好努力讀<br />\n點解要我成個暑假都要我對住你<br />\n我好愛你<br />\n但係行唔到落去<br />\n你咁堅決做反朋友<br />\n到底我地仲有無可能一齊反<br />\n<br />\n為自己set一個限期 兩個半月後嘅生日<br />\n唔知可唔可以令你愛反我<br />\n定係我會真係放棄<br />\n好想講<br />\n我真係好愛你<br />\n就算呢年幾有幾難行都好<br />\n對我幾差都好<br />\n我都愛你<br />\n無後悔過 因為係我揀咗同你一齊<br />\n到依家 我只係希望我地可以重新認識 重新開始"},{"pid":"5ce94dbdd93e118a8780f51741bc62d99c6610de","tid":2069761,"uid":158899,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/06/18/234044_1634493e55e411027edd8d07769fa00e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F06%2F18%2F234044_1634493e55e411027edd8d07769fa00e.gif&h=cf239710&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58f4c89d4e7147fe024f7816042865b117f7dc43","tid":2069761,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:42:19.000Z","msg":"快啲收皮啦！"},{"pid":"02e4193d5e3957c6a4213b1088329e15776b59df","tid":2069761,"uid":191846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:48:04.000Z","msg":"裂左咪搵人痴返囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1153374dc038a215876834e36d76ec3806847bdd","tid":2069761,"uid":203701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T15:58:38.000Z","msg":"C打 睇過下你啲舊post<br />\n你嘅愛唔應該咁廉價㗎 Take care"},{"pid":"a4b864de041594fa68f012afa0ebc22579fdf157","tid":2069761,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T16:38:47.000Z","msg":"洗啦"},{"pid":"0b060035cc